room_title: Escape room " Murder Mystery Train" by Mission Escape Rooms in Annapolis
room_description: Murder has brought you and your team of investigators aboard the Cryptique Express. Once a lavish train ride across Europe, now has become a puzzling crime scene. Your suspects? A group of various wealthy passengers known to have visited the victim’s cabin the night before. It’s a race against time as you search for clues to catch the culprit before the train reaches it’s final destination and the killer gets away for good!
